The Sage - Powers and Rules

Flight
	Buff
	Reduce Attack damage taken by 50%. Cancelled if dealt Attack damage X times in one turn.
Brew
	You obtain a Potion in X turns, either now (X=0) or at the start of that turn. If you don't have empty potion slots at that point, you choose which potions to keep.
Brewing (Buff)	
	You brew potions X turns faster.
Disoriented (Debuff)
	The first Attack of this Enemy has no effect, for X turns.
Thirsty (Debuff)
	Receives 50% more damage from potions, for X turns.


Gaining Artifacts is not considered a debuff.